://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> 3.5716 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001252\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001252\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> Moretti 1968-1990 787 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000015\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000015\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>  \u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":557,"html":558},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[560,562],{"image":82,"thumb":561,"title":83},"ISic003246_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":433,"thumb":563,"title":83},"ISic003246-thumb.jpg"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
